From 2191c3c49bd0092ba000b22ec60a3d9ede3cb58e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: kosti <koshdot@proton.me>
Date: Sat, 7 Mar 2026 23:40:49 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 03/13] feat: add Nomen memory backend integration
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Add nomen as path dependency
- nomen_adapter.rs: Memory trait impl via Nomen API (lazy async init)
- nomen_migrate.rs: SQLite → Nomen migration CLI (migrate-to-nomen --dry-run)
- contextvm_bridge.rs: Context-VM wired into daemon serve loop
- Register Nomen variant in memory factory
